                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9043" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1366</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">985 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国有控股甲公司参股民营丙公司是战略发展需要吗？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Is It Necessary for State-controlled Company A&#39;s Strategic Development to Invest in Private Enterprise C?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李艳，田晓庆</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">兰州理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">甲股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">石油工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">29 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">混合所有制；长期股权投资；企业估值；自由现金流折现；公司治理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Mixed ownership; Long-term equity investment; Firm valuation; Discounted FCF model; Corporate governance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023年5月，甲公司收到深交所对其2022年报中“关于对丙公司长期股权投资计提6000万元减值准备”的监管问询；在对深交所做出回复的5天后，甲公司注册地证监局进驻公司进行现场调查，约谈资产评估师和年审会计师，调阅资产评估工作底稿；2个月后，中纪委介入调查。本案例阐述了甲公司发展中遇到的困境及对丙公司股权投资的决策过程，用较为翔实的数据资料呈现了对丙公司的估值以及长期股权投资的确认与计量，旨在通过对股权投资对象的选择、股权投资核算等问题的探讨，引导学员认识财务会计核算并不是单纯的技术问题，而是与企业所处经济环境、行业特征、发展战略、业务模式等因素密切相关；决策不慎可能导致国有资产流失。通过案例研讨，培养学员识别、分析国企混合所有制改革中会计决策的经济后果，探寻国有资产流失的路径及治理措施。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In May 2023, Company A received a regulatory inquiry from SZSE about &quot;Impairment of long-term equity investment in Company C of 60 million yuan&quot; in its 2022 annual report. Five days after replying to the regulatory inquiry, the Securities Regulatory Bureau to which Company A is registered conducted on-site investigation, interviewed the asset appraisers and annual report auditors, and reviewed the working papers of asset appraisal.Two months later, CPC Central Commission for Discipline Inspection intervened in the investigation. The case expounds the difficulties encountered in the development of Company A and the decision-making process of equity investment in Company C, and presents the valuation of Company C and the confirmation and measurement of long-term equity investment with more detailed information, aiming at guiding students to understand that financial accounting is not purely techniques, but closely related to factors such as the economic environment, industry characteristics, development strategy and business model of the enterprise. Imprudent decision-making may lead to the loss of state-owned assets. The case also aims to train students to identify and analyze the economic consequences of accounting decisions in the reform of mixed ownership, and to explore the path and governance measures of the loss of state-owned assets.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《财务会计学》、《财务管理理论与实务》、《资产评估学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业价值评估；自由现金流折现；长期股权投资减值；管理者过度自信；政治寻租；国有资产流失路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
